summary: Jester R. Bryant, 1.D., Sc. D., was born September 8, 1930, in ronisville, Kentucky. He is married with two child, and is a Surgeon at the University of Cincinnati. Jester was a member of Phi Beta Kappa and Pi Kappa Epsilon societies.
